# Bilal Video Studio — environment
#
# You do NOT need to set anything here. All API keys are entered in the app's
# Settings screen and stored locally in ./data. These optional overrides exist
# only for advanced setups.

# Override where local data (SQLite + render files) is stored.
# Defaults to the project's ./data folder.
# BILAL_DATA_DIR=

# Use a specific ffmpeg binary instead of the bundled one.
# FFMPEG_PATH=
